column2: SELECT top # plate, fiberid, mjd, z, snmedian, h_beta_flux, h_beta_flux_err,  h_alpha_flux, h_alpha_flux_err, oiii_#_flux, oiii_#_flux_err,  nii_#_flux, nii_#_flux_err, sii_#_flux, sii_#_flux_err,  sii_#_flux, sii_#_flux_err, subclass, class FROM GalSpecLine as G JOIN SpecObjall as S  ON S.specobjid = G.specobjid WHERE S.class = &&& and S.SNmedian > # and  S.z < # and S.zwarning = #  and G.h_beta_flux_err > # and  G.h_beta_flux > #*G.h_beta_flux_err  and G.h_alpha_flux_err > # and  G.h_alpha_flux > #*G.h_alpha_flux_err  and G.oiii_#_flux_err > # and  G.oiii_#_flux > #* G.oiii_#_flux_err  and G.nii_#_flux_err > # and  G.nii_#_flux > #*G.nii_#_flux_err  and (S.subclass = &&& or  S.subclass = &&&)
